This paper deals with wireless communication systems and optimization problems related to power control and spectral efficiency. Therefore, the most likely category is cs.IT (Information Theory). The paper also involves wireless power transfer, which falls under the category of cs.NI (Networking and Internet Architecture). The optimization problem is related to system-level performance, which can be categorized under cs.SY (Systems and Control). The paper also deals with massive MIMO systems, which can be categorized under cs.MM (Multimedia). Finally, the paper involves optimization problems related to fairness, which can be categorized under cs.GT (Computer Science and Game Theory).
